{"tid":1027877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片︰鬧市狂奔 熱血男追手機賊","createTime":"2019-02-19T05:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T06:39:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"acb31c6491a1536bcc68eb104466a0f0c25a1d19","tid":1027877,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190219/20615976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F20615976&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEt%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=73a33442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F20615976&h=3a6efb83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190219/20615976</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片︰鬧市狂奔 熱血男追手機賊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190219/large/1550508963_0781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190219%2Flarge%2F1550508963_0781.jpg&h=4d1f7bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賊人盜竊事敗，遭熱心男途人（右）截停。 讀者提供 圖片<br />\n<br />\n一名中年賊膽大包天，昨中午12時許在觀塘開源道街頭，偷走一名25歲女途人一部價值約4,500元的手機，得手後拔足逃走。女事主即時發現大驚呼叫，一名熱心男途人聞聲協助追截，其後在成業街將疑人截停。市民袁小姐目擊經過，指熱心男捉實賊人不放，「賊人仲作勢出拳想打人」，熱心男沒有退縮，更喝斥賊人「搶人嘢仲想打我，咁惡」。<br />\n<br />\n此時圍觀市民越來越多，有人協助報警，賊人見勢色不對一度求饒：「放開我，我唔會走！」熱心男不為所動，其後警員趕至，以涉嫌盜竊拘捕58歲姓李男子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n爆相畀$500、爆片送$1,000嘅基本獎賞外，仲會選出每周之星，每星期最高單日總點擊頭5名即刻科水$10,000，而每月15號至翌月14號期間獲得全月最高單日總點擊者，更可以成為每月盟主，額外獎賞$100,000，係$100,000！爆相爆片必須為本報獨家採用，一經刊登立即有獎！<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片WhatsApp：6383 6568<br />\n參加細則<br />\n1.爆相爆片必須由參加者拍攝。<br />\n2.若本報發現任何造假情況，將取消其參賽資格。<br />\n3.壹傳媒集團員工及親屬不可參加。<br />\n4.本報會保留採用爆相爆片與否和獎項分配的一切權利，如有任何爭議，以本報決定為準。<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港鐵道歉 聲稱誤會"},{"pid":"bcececc516dfcbccb73692251de7d70750421a34","tid":1027877,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"圍觀市民越來越多"},{"pid":"509b2b52a1b1f2ecafb09198b2bcf5e3de2ba8f5","tid":1027877,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"段片咁耐都係得一個男出手<br />\n其他..."},{"pid":"66ed9091b4aa004fd10a8b5015638a167f1d9a7e","tid":1027877,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"條女應該幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9c32713eae183f2dcfc55dae6b273e7ccdb83d","tid":1027877,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ed9091b4aa004fd10a8b5015638a167f1d9a7e","tid":1027877,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"條女應該幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"之後佢地食飯 之後 已經拎正牌想揸佢要揸概野"},{"pid":"7966c12719d77901e7c6a22334ca39254bf8671a","tid":1027877,"uid":104830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"追撚爆佢老母臭閪啦死賊仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af46b592c632a0fc82e8d5ed6e9a9822207c831d","tid":1027877,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"成個賊佬樣"},{"pid":"5a1513d5a66736ff930c785fb7c7902b0fafa8ec","tid":1027877,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"條友三行佬黎"}]}